Difficulty getting >30 valid ensembles near edges within reasonable time frame with ‘Water depth source: Bottom Track’. Strategy was to use ‘Water depth source: Bottom Track’ for the standard 40sec or until a depth was detected and then switch to ‘Water depth source: Manual Depth’ and enter the detected depth.
